OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry at first
OL,6,Fthis evening across the north and east
OL,7,Fwith some frost. Rain will soon spread
OL,8,Fto the west coast this evening, then
OL,9,Fpatchy rain spreading east across most
OL,10,Fareas by midnight. Then drier in the
OL,11,Fearly hours.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSunday:FAfter a dry start, rain will
OL,14,Fspread northeast across all parts in
OL,15,Fthe morning. Then becoming drier but
OL,16,Ffurther rain spreading to the south
OL,17,Flate afternoon. Windy in west.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
