OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FRain
OL,6,Fclearing away on Monday morning, then
OL,7,Fbrighter with a few showers. Dry on
OL,8,FMonday and Tuesday with overnight
OL,9,Ffrost.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
